#                                                      EDITORS                                                        #
# ==================================================================================================================== #
# --- JetBrains (PyCharm/IntelliJ) ---
# Ignore everything in .idea by default...
.idea/*
# ...but allow sharing a few project-level, team-useful settings:
!.idea/.gitignore
!.idea/codeStyles/
!.idea/inspectionProfiles/
!.idea/runConfigurations/

# Rationale:
# - codeStyles/             -> shared code style (kept minimal; EditorConfig already covers most)
# - inspectionProfiles/     -> shared inspections
# - runConfigurations/      -> run/debug configs that point to repo files, not user paths

# --- VS Code ---
# Ignore everything in .vscode by default...
.vscode/*
# ...but allow sharing safe, project-scoped files:
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json

# Rationale:
# - settings.json            -> only project-safe settings (e.g., .venv path, Ruff on save)
# - extensions.json          -> recommended extensions for the workspace
# - tasks.json / launch.json -> shared tasks & debug configs

